"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"### Send Token Ibc\\n\\nTransfer a token asset between Cosmos blockchain networks.\\n\\n#### Method Declaration\\n\\n:::code-group\\n\\n```python [Python]\\n\\n```\\n\\n```rust [Rust]\\npub async fn send_token_ibc(\\n    &mut self,\\n    account: &mut Account,\\n    sender: Address,\\n    recipient: Address,\\n    token: impl Tokenized,\\n    source_channel: String,\\n) -> Result<TxHash, Error>\\n```\\n\\n```typescript [TypeScript]\\nasync IBCTransfer(message: MsgTransferEncodeObject): Promise<DeliverTxResponse>\\n\\nasync send(\\n    messages: EncodeObject[],\\n    gasPrice: GasPrice = GasPrice.fromString('0.1uusdc'),\\n    memo?: string,\\n): Promise<DeliverTxResponse>\\n```\\n\\n```url [API]\\n/ibc.applications.transfer.v1.Msg/Transfer\\n```\\n\\n:::\\n\\n:::details[Unification Plan]\\n\\n- Generalize to all IBC/blockchains.\\n- Missing in Python.\\n- Missing in TS: user required to produce the low-level message and then `post.send()` it.\\n  :::\\n\\n#### Parameters\\n\\n| Parameter        | Location | Type      | Mandatory | Description                        |\\n| ---------------- | -------- | --------- | --------- | ---------------------------------- |\\n| `account`        | query    | [Account] | true      | The account.                       |\\n| `sender`         | query    | [Address] | true      | Address of the sender.             |\\n| `recipient`      | query    | [Address] | true      | Address of the recipient.          |\\n| `token`          | query    | int       | true      | Token type and amount to transfer. |\\n| `source_channel` | query    | String    | true      | Source IBC relay channel.          |\\n\\n#### Response\\n\\n| Status | Meaning       | Schema   |                                       |\\n| ------ | ------------- | -------- | ------------------------------------- |\\n| `200`  | [OK]          | [TxHash] |                                       |\\n| `400`  | [Bad Request] |          | The request was malformed or invalid. |\\n\\n[OK]: /types/ok\\n[Account]: /types/account\\n[Address]: /types/address\\n[Tokenized]: /types/tokenized\\n[Bad Request]: /types/bad-request\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/noble-client/send_token_ibc#send-token-ibc\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Transfer a token asset between Cosmos blockchain networks.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/noble-client/send_token_ibc.mdx#send-token-ibc\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nTransfer a token asset between Cosmos blockchain networks.\\n\",\"title\":\"Send Token Ibc\",\"titles\":[null,null]},{\"href\":\"/noble-client/send_token_ibc#method-declaration\",\"html\":\"\\n<div class=\\\"code-group\\\"><div data-title=\\\"Python\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Python\\\" data-lang=\\\"python\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"Rust\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"Rust\\\" data-lang=\\\"rust\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">pub</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> async</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> fn</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\"> send_token_ibc</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">    &amp;mut</span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\"> self</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    account</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> &amp;mut</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Account</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    sender</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Address</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    recipient</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Address</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    token</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\"> impl</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Tokenized</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    source_channel</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">:</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> String</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">) </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">-&gt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\"> Result</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">TxHash</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">, </span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#F69D50\\\">Error</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"TypeScript\\\"><pre class=\\\"shiki shiki-themes github-light github-dark-dimmed\\\" style=\\\"background-color:#fff;--shiki-dark-bg:#22272e;color:#24292e;--shiki-dark:#adbac7\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" data-title=\\\"TypeScript\\\" data-lang=\\\"typescript\\\"><code><span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">async </span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">IBCTransfer</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(message: MsgTransferEncodeObject): </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">Promise</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">DeliverTxResponse</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\" data-empty-line=\\\"true\\\"> </span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">async </span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">send</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    messages: EncodeObject[],</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    gasPrice: GasPrice </span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">=</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> GasPrice.</span><span style=\\\"color:#6F42C1;--shiki-dark:#DCBDFB\\\">fromString</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">(</span><span style=\\\"color:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#96D0FF\\\">&#x27;0.1uusdc&#x27;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">),</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">    memo</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">?:</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\"> string,</span></span>\\n<span class=\\\"line\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">): </span><span style=\\\"color:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#6CB6FF\\\">Promise</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&lt;</span><span style=\\\"color:#24292E;--shiki-dark:#ADBAC7\\\">DeliverTxResponse</span><span style=\\\"color:#D73A49;--shiki-dark:#F47067\\\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><div data-title=\\\"API\\\"><pre><code class=\\\"language-url\\\">/ibc.applications.transfer.v1.Msg/Transfer\\n</code></pre></div></div>\\n<details><summary>Unification Plan</summary><ul>\\n<li>Generalize to all IBC/blockchains.</li>\\n<li>Missing in Python.</li>\\n<li>Missing in TS: user required to produce the low-level message and then <code>post.send()</code> it.</li>\\n</ul></details>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/noble-client/send_token_ibc.mdx#method-declaration\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n pub async fn send_token_ibc(\\n    &amp;mut self,\\n    account: &amp;mut Account,\\n    sender: Address,\\n    recipient: Address,\\n    token: impl Tokenized,\\n    source_channel: String,\\n) -&gt; Result&lt;TxHash, Error&gt;async IBCTransfer(message: MsgTransferEncodeObject): Promise&lt;DeliverTxResponse&gt;\\n \\nasync send(\\n    messages: EncodeObject[],\\n    gasPrice: GasPrice = GasPrice.fromString(&#x27;0.1uusdc&#x27;),\\n    memo?: string,\\n): Promise&lt;DeliverTxResponse&gt;/ibc.applications.transfer.v1.Msg/Transfer\\n\\nUnification Plan\\nGeneralize to all IBC/blockchains.\\nMissing in Python.\\nMissing in TS: user required to produce the low-level message and then post.send() it.\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Method Declaration\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Send Token Ibc\"]},{\"href\":\"/noble-client/send_token_ibc#parameters\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Location</th><th>Type</th><th>Mandatory</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>account</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/account\\\">Account</a></td><td>true</td><td>The account.</td></tr><tr><td><code>sender</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/address\\\">Address</a></td><td>true</td><td>Address of the sender.</td></tr><tr><td><code>recipient</code></td><td>query</td><td><a href=\\\"/types/address\\\">Address</a></td><td>true</td><td>Address of the recipient.</td></tr><tr><td><code>token</code></td><td>query</td><td>int</td><td>true</td><td>Token type and amount to transfer.</td></tr><tr><td><code>source_channel</code></td><td>query</td><td>String</td><td>true</td><td>Source IBC relay channel.</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/noble-client/send_token_ibc.mdx#parameters\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nParameterLocationTypeMandatoryDescriptionaccountqueryAccounttrueThe account.senderqueryAddresstrueAddress of the sender.recipientqueryAddresstrueAddress of the recipient.tokenqueryinttrueToken type and amount to transfer.source_channelqueryStringtrueSource IBC relay channel.\\n\",\"title\":\"Parameters\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Send Token Ibc\"]},{\"href\":\"/noble-client/send_token_ibc#response\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Schema</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>200</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/ok\\\">OK</a></td><td>[TxHash]</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><code>400</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/bad-request\\\">Bad Request</a></td><td></td><td>The request was malformed or invalid.</td></tr></tbody></table>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/noble-client/send_token_ibc.mdx#response\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nStatusMeaningSchema200OK[TxHash]400Bad RequestThe request was malformed or invalid.\",\"title\":\"Response\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Send Token Ibc\"]}]}}"
